name: Jane's Mazes v0.1.0
description:
In this game, Jane, a young princess who loves balloons, finds herself in a maze of spikes! You need to help her navigate through these spike mazes to get herself out!

As of now, this game is very early in development, with only 2 levels and a title screen, plus no credits or music. Hope to continue updating in the future.
